### Feature Description

I suggest add a small middleware:

```
func ByHost(mapping map[string]fiber.Handler) fiber.Handler {
	return func(ctx fiber.Ctx) error {
		handler, ok := mapping[ctx.Host()]
		if !ok {
			return ctx.Next()
		}

		return handler(ctx)
	}
}
```

Useful for `inner-api` handlers

